headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. To Speak at S&P Global Ratings' 2025 Annual Insurance Conference and Host Regularly Scheduled Quarterly Investor Meeting
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (NYSE: AJG) today announced that J. Patrick Gallagher Jr., Chairman and CEO, will be participating in a Broker CEO fireside chat at S&P Global Ratings' 2025 Annual Insurance Conference on Thursday, June 5, 2025.

headline: GTCR investors set to reap over $5 billion as exits pile, source says
summary: Private equity firm GTCR is set toreturn more than $5 billion to its investors in the calendaryear, a source familiar with the matter told Reuters onThursday, after a string of strong exits sealed...
